FORTIM, A LITTLE-KNOWN PARADISE

. The Time Property Club is located at Pontal de Maceió beach, in Fortim (CE).
. It’s a charming fishermen village in the interior of Ceará.
. 115 km from Fortaleza (1 hour drive on highway CE-040).
. 15 km from Aracati international Airport. 20 km from the beaches in Canoa Quebrada.
. Approximately 1 hour drive from Beach Park, one of the best water parks in Latin America.

AND WITH A PERFECT NATURE

. It’s summmer all year round.
. Beaches with warm, crystal clear waters
. Surrounded by the Jaguaribe River, with more than 35 navigable kilometers.
. A perfect ecosystem for resting, strolling or playing water sports.
